Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Trick them and snatch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:06.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji returns to the silver screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:12.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And we give you loyal anime watchers a sneak peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:16.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win. For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:22.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's actor, Tatsuya Fujiwara, appears in the next episode of the anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:23.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}This is awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:25.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}There's so many people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:32.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll play that tender man in black comics fans know so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who? Who?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:39.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:41.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}Stand up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:45.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:49.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}Perfect. You nailed it in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:50.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:54.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes peeled for the scene he nailed, next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:59.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}Seeing that scene again will be shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:02.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}I hope you all enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:09.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya Fujiwara stars in Kaiji 2: Jinsei Dakkai Game, this November 5th!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:21.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ultimate barrier rises from nowhere to bar Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:19.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突如 カイジの前に立ちふさがった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:24.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,究極の壁　｢風のカーテン｣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:24.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A curtain of wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:27.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:31.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}Bitter Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ　カイジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:33.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:46.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　降りろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,触るな　待て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:47.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:50.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait! Just hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:53.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've still got money!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:54.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金はまだあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I still have the 800 thou I came up with with!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:58.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下を出る時 受け取った80万が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:01.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I spent a little bit, but there's still 720 left!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと使っちまったが 72万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:07.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This... I can keep playing with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:07.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでまだ打てるはず　これで…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何しやがる！\Nハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:19.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No. No, you can't. Not with pocket change like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメダメ　打てません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな はした金では
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want to buy Paqy for the Bog, you've got to cough up at least three mil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼のパッキーは最低300万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そこを何とか　バラ売りで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:27.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on! Just sell me one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:31.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll kindly be on your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お引き取りを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:36.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:36.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　降りろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:43.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か 助けろ！金を…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Money! Just lend me a little money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を貸せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に あと少し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:50.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I almost got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと少しなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit more, and I'll have it beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少しで攻略なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can see that, can't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:57.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるだろ？\N誰でも… 誰でもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:56.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anything! Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just lend me some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:59.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貸せ　つぎ込め 俺に！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Invest in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me another chance to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺で勝負しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か 俺で勝負しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Take a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:15.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わっちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒ　イヒ　イヒ　イヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:31.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か！俺で勝負を　勝負を…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:30.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Somebody take a chance on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てやっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:39.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あり得ないんだよ そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:42.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が貸すか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:45.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell would lend you money after a performance like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負け犬に！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To a loser like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:51.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたんだよ お前は！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:54.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズ　破産　破産だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:52.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破産！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:57.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条はん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたは ひどい人や
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:24.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この声…\N何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:29.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—The last penny a man has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際 なけなしの金\N最後の金っちゅうもんは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？\Nこの声…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:36.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is his last glimmer of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人間にとって\Nまさに命のともしび
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:41.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きる希望そのもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The only hope left in his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:48.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you use this monster to steal it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをあんたは奪ってきたんや
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:49.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この怪物で無慈悲に！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:51.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the rules of the game. Fair's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の結果だ　正当な…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正当やない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:59.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You could flip this thing over, and not one ball would come rolling out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:59.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは逆さに降っても\N玉１つ こぼれん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It really is the devil's own machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう悪魔の台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you know this better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが一番よく知っとるはずや
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dozens of men...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:11.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何十人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:16.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, their families too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや その家族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,縁者を入れれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:27.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Man-Eating Bog must have devoured the hopes, the very lives, of over a hundred people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:20.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100に届こうっちゅう人間が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:25.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この人食い沼によって\N最後の望みを絶たれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでいった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら… 自ら！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:31.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,By their own hands! Their own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… 知るか そんな話！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:41.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each and every one of these silver balls gathered here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに たまっている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:41.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,銀玉その１つ１つが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:53.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is a tear! A tear formed from their regret and resentment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで涙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:47.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,散っていった人間たちの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔恨　怨嗟の涙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:54.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その結晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a deadly sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:06:00.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,罪深い話や　つくづく…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh so deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:03.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万死に値する！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you'll burn for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're not just playing for ourselves here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負は\Nわしらだけのもんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:14.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're playing for everyone who's lost it all to the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:15.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この沼によって散っていった\N数多の破産者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're fighting to give their souls rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人間たちの無念を\N晴らす戦いや
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We have to avenge them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:23.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たにゃならん！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何としても勝つんや！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We have to win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:33.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why I brought the rest of that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:31.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのために持ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき放った金が1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And another ten million here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに ここに1000万や！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Twenty million all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:41.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,都合2000万を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:42.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:46.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！この金で打て 敵を！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:46.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take this money, and take our vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:55.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Make that devil spit up every dirty cent it's swallowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:51.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この悪魔の不当な蓄え　収奪金を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部 吐き出させろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:07:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん　おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:02.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに いつまで待ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you done yet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:10.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放せ　金は… 金ならここにある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:10.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If it's money you want, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing to complain about now, Ichijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文句はねえだろ　一条！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right, Ichijou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:22.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろ　一条！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さん\Nカイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:32.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:35.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん\N起死回生のファインプレーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you didn't cover me there, I'd be dead meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金… 例のあれだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:39.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You went back to the well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正解　社長は出張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:43.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The boss was out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:49.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おまけに今日は日曜で会社は休み\Nツイとった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:47.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Sunday, so there's no one else around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I just took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:51.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You really are something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:51.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をいけしゃあしゃあと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:55.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１度ならず２度までも\Nひどいガードマンだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Going back for more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a terrible guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:58.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about? I'm just borrowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言う　ちょっと借りただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,返せば何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is bring it back, and no one will even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:06.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:06.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ったく　そのとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A miraculous turnaround!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:10.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさに起死回生　土壇場のカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, on the gallows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:14.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ど… どうぞ\N地獄の淵からの生還！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:14.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He returns alive from the bowels of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく そのとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん！\Nそうだ　まだ終わってねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張れ！\Nあきらめるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:33.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:36.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　勝つこと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I win, then everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば問題ない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば すべて正しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:44.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I win, that solves everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きれいに解決する
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:51.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:54.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は… 勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I. Will. Win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:07.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな不運　ツキのなさに\N見舞われても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:09.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care how unlucky I am! I don't care how I feel! I'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決してあきらめない　ねじふせる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll turn everything around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:16.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter if I'm doomed, no matter what's happening, no matter what's in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪の運命　境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:20.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらゆる障害　不平　不満
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:19.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if I hate it! Even if I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:25.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll turn everything around and win in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてをねじふせる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:37.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は そのために生きている！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He wins to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きるために勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He lives to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:47.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つために生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:51.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The game resumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負 再開！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll make it through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗り越える
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll defend my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:10.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の人生をふさぐ この絶望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:17.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord5}Even as this despair closes in on me, chokes me, closes the path before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:15.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を押さえつけ 締めつけ\N道を閉ざす
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:18.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のしかかる障害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の未来を潰し\Nふさごうとしているこの峰を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:26.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As this peak threatens to snuff out my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,越える
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I will overcome it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:39.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The summit is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頂はすぐそこ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right in front of my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐ目の前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！\Nいけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:01.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please, please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:11:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　頼む　頼む…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 見ろよ\N何だよ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,す… すげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異様な光景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An unthinkable sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次々と３段目クルーンに\N送り込まれる玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:18.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Balls rolls into the third tray, one after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They leave an unthinkable sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが異様な光景を生む
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:26.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,埋め尽くす玉　玉　玉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:26.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Balls, balls, balls! They bury the tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right. You don't need to leap for me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　もう飛ぶまでもねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押せ　押してねじ込め！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Push! Shove it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押せ！\N押せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:44.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's this? What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんだよ これは？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The guard of wind is as sure as one of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:48.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風のガードは鉄板　鉄のガード
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:52.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter how many balls there are, not one can get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,銀玉など いくら来ても\Nはじき返せる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いわば砦からの機銃掃射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:59.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like machine gunfire raining down on infantrymen from a fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要塞 対 歩兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:02.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It should be a lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント勝てる勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:07.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But in in this kind of situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが この異常事態！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,膨大すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They don't even die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:20.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも こいつらは死なない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're immortal soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:23.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死がふさがってる兵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:27.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous! It's nothing I ever could have predicted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:27.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　想定外　こんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:32.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At this rate, it doesn't matter where the balls roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:32.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままいけば\Nもう玉の軌道もクソもない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:35.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敷き詰めた玉が玉を押し
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:39.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll spread out on the tray and push themselves straight in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:41.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直接　直接…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:48.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The wind can't hold that many back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの\N風なんかで押し返せるわけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった　カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:18.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A draw! A draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き分け… 引き分けだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き分けで手を打とう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's call it a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:23.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残らせてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:26.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll let {\i1}you{\i0} live!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を特別に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:28.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遅い！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:30.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a day late and a dollar short, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう… 遅い！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:38.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む！そこを… そこを何とか！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:38.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遅い！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離れろ　近づくな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get away! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！\N離れろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:45.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:48.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何や？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:00.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,台が鳴り出した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:03.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:03.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼が鳴き出しおった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうこった こりゃあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が 断末魔ってやつか？これが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:20.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's its death rattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:24.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dying scream of this demonic Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:24.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この悪魔　沼の断末魔か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:28.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘ　どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:31.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Does that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずいぶんと苦しそうじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この悪魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:34.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ド悪魔め！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:36.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You fucking devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:41.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吐き出せ　そんなに出したきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:43.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want to cry that much, then spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吐き出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:53.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The lives of everyone that you devoured!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:53.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が食ってきた人間たちの\Nその命を！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:58.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their hope, despair, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:58.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望　絶望　そのすべてを！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Throw it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吐き出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:14.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時 満ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The breaking point has been reached!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:17.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飽和状態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,包み込まれた当たり穴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The jackpot hole is enveloped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the critical moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臨界点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:39.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Push! Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押せ　押せ　押せ　押せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:43.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ　やめてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:43.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:47.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:50.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please, stop, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめて　頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Push! Push it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:58.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押せ　押し殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:01.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ　やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:07.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! Stop!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔　終わりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's over, devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神さま
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:46.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:57.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:11.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい おい… 入ったよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:10.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It went in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎\N遠藤はん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:29.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入った　入賞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:33.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たり！\N大当たり！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たり！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　カイジ　カイジ\Nカイジ　カイジ　カイジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:47.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　何や？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光り出した　沼が！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:52.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:55.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog is.. The Bog is—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼が！\N沼が光り出した！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog is shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:06.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開く　すべての希望をはねつけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:11.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It opens! All their hope, their struggle, their fears, their suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抗い 飲み込み
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:14.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,固く… 固く閉ざされていた\N悪魔の口が！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:15.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,From the mouth of the demon, once clamped shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解放！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It all flows forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:34.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解放！解放！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:37.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It flows forth! It flows forth! It flows forth!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解放！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解放だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's letting it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,至る所が…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開いてる　ガバガバ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's opening up all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっげえ広いわ 台　入れ放題だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like a playroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出る！出る！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at them all come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひと玉 4000円がいくらでも！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thousands of 4000-yen balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,至福　パチンカーの夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:12.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pure bliss! A pachinko player's fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:16.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん　ドル箱だ\Nドル箱 持ってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops! Go get the ball trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:16.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get me some ball trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:18.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:20.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう　分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:26.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy! Delight! Avaricious bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恍惚　歓喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:26.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,垂涎の至福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,喜々として働く坂崎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:31.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki, a joyful laborer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:32.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,至福の雑用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:36.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh only stands and watches!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:36.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤　ただ突っ立っているだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A blissful observer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,至福の傍観
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji shares their euphoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 カイジも至福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:47.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桃源郷をさまようがごとくの\N圧倒的 至福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:47.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Overwhelming bliss, as if he trod Paradise for just one moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're released!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも狂喜乱舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Underground, sheer revelry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:59.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy! Delight! Tears of gratitude! Weeping! Passion! Gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:55.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,咆哮　歓喜　感涙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嗚咽　感動　感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的 感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Overwhelming gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:07.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この大当たりにより\Nカイジは なし得たのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:06.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With this, Kaiji has succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:11.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has won the 45s the miracle of freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４５組 奇跡の救出を！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:14.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad... You were right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:15.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,父さん…\N父さんの言ったとおりだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:16.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:19.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは… カイジさんは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さんざ引っ張って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't tolerate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何じゃ この決着は！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How did you let this happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸くそ悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:36.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm disgusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:39.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズが！\Nあんなゴミに足をすくわれおって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:41.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were beaten by scum! Trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:43.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使えん　とことん使えん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:43.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Completely useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He makes me sick to my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:45.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘドが出るわ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:48.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうなった以上 何の躊躇もない\N地下行きだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:50.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's going underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:55.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か地下懲役の目安は… おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And what's the rate for underground labor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:55.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ はい　ええと その
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:22:01.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's, er, fifteen years per ten million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:01.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万で15年でございます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:08.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　なら奴が帝愛に与えた\N７億の損害は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:07.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Since he lost Teiai 700 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:11.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,15 years by 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:11.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,15年の70倍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1050年 地下行きだ！
